@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_lwicrc(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.exp(0.94)
    v2 = wp.abs((tmp * 0.37))
    v1 = v0
    v1 = ((wp.exp(v0 + 0.58) + (v2 + 0.01 - v2 + 0.98)) / wp.cos(v1))
    data[tid] = v0
